Howard Stein Hudson (commonly abbreviated as HSH, formerly Howard/Stein-Hudson Associates, Inc.) is a multidisciplinary American civil engineering consulting and design firm headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts with offices throughout the state. The company was founded in 1987 by Jane Howard and Kathy Stein-Hudson.
